<figureCitation id="8B34E2367EA8D6DD78A13E1E4A0ACA40" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Poa iconia var. iconia. A whole plant B spikelet, lateral view C close-up of inflorescence. Images A, C of V. R. Clark &amp; C. Kelly 269 (GRA 0009104) B of V. R. Clark &amp; C. Kelly 269 (PRE)." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.165.55948.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/468631" pageId="0" pageNumber="27">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
